# auto re-tile icons when list changes
AddToFunc TileIcons
+ "C" Iconify off
+ "C" All (CurrentPage, Iconic) PlaceAgain Icon

AddToFunc Move-or-Raise
+ "I" Raise
+ "M" Move
+ "D" Lower

AddToFunc Resize-or-Raise
+ "M" Raise
+ "M" Resize
+ "D" Lower

# double click max, single click move
AddToFunc Maximize-or-Move
+ "D" Maximize
+ "I" Raise
+ "C" Focus
+ "M" Move

AddToFunc WinTileRight
+ "I" Maximize 884p 1074p
+ "I" Move -145p -5p

AddToFunc WinTileLeft
+ "I" Maximize 884p 1074p
+ "I" Move +3p -5p

AddToFunc WinTileBottomRight
+ "I" Maximize 884p 530p
+ "I" Move -145p -5p

AddToFunc WinTileUpperRight
+ "I" Maximize 884p 530p
+ "I" Move -145p -549p

